[2020-12-09 01:56] velizar_ (Name): 2: Normally the first few attackers for you get no value while you're below absorb; however in case of e.g. doomed mech or mahar, when you build your 4 attackers and your opponent builds that absorber, then the existence of your last 2 attackers encourages your opponent to attack you for 2 less, so they are giving value for you; 
They are giving you less than full value, because they are allowing your opponent to threaten without attacking (thus making your opponent's absorber-attacker more valuable than if simply attacking).
